  <brief_title>Effect of Peritoneal Lavage With Clindamycin-Gentamicin Solution &amp; Oncologic Outcome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Peritoneal Lavage With Clindamycin-Gentamicin Solution During Elective Colorectal Cancer Surgery on the Oncologic Outcome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
